#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_gradienttexture.rst:14
msgid "Gradient-filled texture."
msgstr "渐变填充纹理。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_gradienttexture.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_gradienttexture.rst:19
msgid ""
"GradientTexture uses a :ref:`Gradient <class_Gradient>` to fill the "
"texture data. The gradient will be filled from left to right using colors"
" obtained from the gradient. This means the texture does not necessarily "
"represent an exact copy of the gradient, but instead an interpolation of "
"samples obtained from the gradient at fixed steps (see :ref:`width "
"<class_GradientTexture_property_width>`)."
msgstr ""
"``GradientTexture`` 使用 :ref:`Gradient <class_Gradient>` "
"填充纹理数据。渐变将被从左到右填充，而填充使用从渐变获得的颜色。这意味着纹理不必代表渐变的一个精确副本，而是以固定步长对从渐变获得的样本进行插值（请参见"
" :ref:`width <class_GradientTexture_property_width>`）。"

